title: Chicago Hope S04E14 - Psychodrama.avi
description:
Watters is on crutches after a basketball injury and thinks he has witnessed a murder. Austin receives a bird from Danny, the electrician she's been dating, which causes havoc in the hospital. Diane believes she has found her birthmother. McNeil is unpleasantly surprised by a visit from his brother. 


More to follow, please give back as much as you take.
